<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA22">
<l>vantitaṉaik koḷvatē yokkumiv vāḷaraviṉ</l>
<l>cintai yatuterintu kāṇmiṉō - vantō</l>
<l>rirānī riruṇṭaṉaiya kaṇṭattī reṅkaḷ</l>
<l>pirāṉīruñ ceṉṉip piṟai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Coming [and] taking it seems the thought of this bright snake</l>
<l>– understand that [and] see – the crescent moon on the head of you our lord,</l>
<l>you with the throat that has come [and] darkened</l>
<l>like the sole essence of night.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
